    id: 'prompt-35',
    prompt: 'Set up automatic investment contributions to a diversified index fund portfolio starting with your next paycheck',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'Automating your investments removes emotion and timing guesswork from wealth building, ensuring consistent progress regardless of market conditions or busy schedules. Choose low-cost broad market index funds that track the total stock market or S&P 500, then set up automatic monthly transfers from your checking account to your investment account. Starting with even $100-200 per month builds the habit and takes advantage of dollar-cost averaging, where you buy more shares when prices are low and fewer when prices are high.'
  }
];</parameter>
